Before editing these files, read:
- `AGENTS.md`
- `.ai/instructions/frontend-react.md`
- `.ai/instructions/coding-style.md`

Rules:
- One material component per file in `components/materials/`.
- New components require render file + protocol file + catalog entry.
- State changes through `editorStore` actions only.
- Monaco Editor is the only code editor — no overlapping alternatives.
